articles.title: Most impressive photos of year from James Webb telescope [PHOTOS] - AzerNews.Az
articles.description: The editors of the American Time magazine have selected the most impressive images taken by the James Webb Space Telescope in the past year and all the photos in the collection were published in 2023, Azernews reports.
